00:10:04,030 --> 00:10:04,360
<font face="YF补 汉仪夏日体" size="48"><b>诶</b></font>

198
00:10:05,200 --> 00:10:06,360
<font face="YF补 汉仪夏日体" size="48"><b>好不容易…</b></font>

199
